{"tid":2464060,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"小粉紅玻璃心又碎了！IU 舊採訪把台灣與中國、日本並列疑「挺台獨」被罵翻","createTime":"2021-03-27T07:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T07:37:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9e37d84860d103bd83f736479a9ae18b725840d3","tid":2464060,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:29:38.000Z","msg":"韓國女星 IU 近日剛發新專輯大受好評，但真的是人紅是非多，稍早有中國網友挖出她之前的訪談，發現她在受訪時提到「各國」的粉絲時，竟然把台灣與中國、日本、印度等並列，疑似「挺台獨」的言論讓小粉紅氣炸了！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2021/03/27/210327-15912-5-xdFXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2021%2F03%2F27%2F210327-15912-5-xdFXg.jpg&h=11530678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就是這一席話，把台灣與中國、日本、印度等國家並列，引起中國網友的不滿，認為IU難道是挺台獨？雖然IU粉絲澄清，她說的不是國家是「地區」，但大部分的中國網友顯然不買單而紛紛開砲：「竟然把台灣跟中國、日本這些國家並列，無語」、「好無力的澄清」、「誰會這樣說」、「翻譯的問題也不該把台灣跟中國並列吧」！<br />\n<br />\n不過台灣和韓國的網友倒是一片叫好，並認為IU只是說了實話，也認為只是習慣稱呼問題，而且是幾年前的採訪又要拿出來講？也被狂酸：「玻璃心又要碎了」、「小粉紅最近好忙」！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2021/03/27/210327-15912-8-hP5rw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2021%2F03%2F27%2F210327-15912-8-hP5rw.jpg&h=4418a4cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://istyle.ltn.com.tw/article/15912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fistyle.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2F15912&d=jrWVSpMJYTM9%2F%2BTkK0Hr39Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=4f9b9e6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fistyle.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2F15912&h=0697572b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://istyle.ltn.com.tw/article/15912</a>"},{"pid":"9c2aa0b127ce36eb3c72e0ce734f7ecc9f2095e0","tid":2464060,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那人真係好撚得閒"},{"pid":"cc0bebd81ee4d722f7f12f4c89c306365cf10cfa","tid":2464060,"uid":104035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:34:20.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲, 又畀韓狗串, 到底國家幾時先可以收返台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0425aa3a7731550509c2be190ad8ae2d5ef9b53e","tid":2464060,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:36:08.000Z","msg":"韓國人都去管埋 辛苦到"},{"pid":"7199441d52da46ad95ba02d60898407baa2e170d","tid":2464060,"uid":128102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/nm9e3jz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fnm9e3jz.jpg&h=42a7a915&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20d67534710622e7896a26a8e6e731b1734b0600","tid":2464060,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:37:19.000Z","msg":"又被台獨<br />\n洗唔洗出黎認係中國人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}